{"tid":2365642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：歡迎拜登政府能重返多邊主義","createTime":"2021-01-14T02:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T07:59:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc9135e530649ca6e9879ecf0bc0f2d3a732b33","tid":2365642,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"王毅：中方歡迎美國新政府能重返多邊主義 <br />\n<br />\n正在印尼訪問的國務委員兼外長王毅表示，國際社會都期待美國新政府能重返多邊主義，中方亦持歡迎態度。王毅說，中方反對以多邊主義為幌子、藉口及意識形態化，搞封閉的集團政治，將少數國家制定的規則強加給國際社會，打造針對特定國家的價值觀同盟。 <br />\n<br />\n王毅強調，只有實行真正多邊主義，才能維護好世界的和平、穩定和發展，推行偽多邊主義，只會製造新的分裂、引發新的衝突，國際社會對此應加以警惕。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2374735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2374735&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=0bb6d176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2374735</a>"},{"pid":"202e60e30dccbd4fd9a6f60018e13b310d3e728e","tid":2365642,"uid":53498,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"代表埋美國講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec03f5fdac5787cf32831a24d0adde98a11ddee4","tid":2365642,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3ec6b64b880aaea3d786a572c587a24d0122c5","tid":2365642,"uid":256837,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"兩黨共sick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df881fe403fe45544aa7e3878184153b3e5fe73","tid":2365642,"uid":55089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"美國果班左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im